title: Protecting Your Energy with Jason Kennedy and Lauren Scruggs Kennedy
description:
Entertainment journalist Jason Kennedy and author-entrepreneur Lauren Scruggs Kennedy shed light on the topic of chronic fatigue, specifically after a life-altering accident. Chelsea and Judah share their own experiences with protecting their energy, and tips on balancing the challenges of an introvert x extrovert relationship.
